

== LibraryStart
A listing of the functions available.
Mostly for testing stuff.
What do you want to do?
+ Resource Gather
    -> resourceGather
+ Look at Inventory
    <- ExamineWhat
+ Cycles & Tasks
    #CLEAR
    -> newCYCLE_DEMO
+ Something else.
    ->YesThisWorks
+ Count Fish
    ->catchFish
+ Dip Switch
    -> count_your_toes
+ Stat Print Avery
    -> StatPrintdemo
